/wiki/Reza_Nasseri: Reza Nasseri ( Persian : رضا ناصری , born 16 September 1975 , in Iran ) is an Iranian futsal player . He is a Goalkeeper , and currently a member of Shahrdari Saveh .
/wiki/Morteza_Azimaei: Morteza Azimaei Divkolaei ( Persian : مرتضی عظیمایی دیوکلایی , born 11 September 1982 ) is an Iranian futsal player .
/wiki/Majid_Latifi: Majid Latifi ( Persian : مجید لطیفی , born 21 March 1981 ) is an Iranian retired futsal player .
/wiki/Mohammad_Hashemzadeh: Mohammad Hashemzadeh ( Persian : محمد هاشم‌زاده , born 27 January 1977 ) is an Iranian futsal coach . He was a Winger .
/wiki/Vahid_Shamsaei: Vahid Shamsaei ( Persian : وحید شمسايی , born 21 September 1975 ) is an Iranian retired futsal player and current coach . He was a Pivot and he scored 392 goals in international matches . Shamsaei has been named AFC Futsal Player of the Year on three occasions ( 2007 , 2008 and 2015 ) . He has also won eight AFC Futsal Championships with Iran . Shamsaei is regarded as the Ali Daei of futsal by the Asian Football Confederation .
/wiki/Mohammad_Taheri: Mohammad Taheri ( Persian : محمد طاهری , born 5 February 1985 ) is an Iranian futsal player . He is a Right Winger , and currently a player of Setaregan Varamin .
/wiki/Majid_Tikdarinejad: Majid Hossein Tikdarinejad ( Persian : مجید حسین تیکدری‌نژاد , born 6 September 1982 ) is an Iranian futsal player . He is a member of Lokomotiv Tashkent and the Iran national futsal team .
/wiki/Mostafa_Nazari: Mostafa Nazari ( Persian : مصطفی نظری ; born 11 December 1982 ) is an Iranian futsal player . He is currently a member of Sunich Saveh in the Iranian Futsal Super League .
/wiki/Futsal_at_the_2005_Asian_Indoor_Ga: Futsal at the 2005 Asian Indoor Games was held in Bangkok , Thailand from 10 November to 17 November 2005 .
/wiki/Mohammad_Akefian: Mohammad Akefian ( born 31 May 1984 ) is an Iranian sprinter specializing in the 400 metres . He won several medals at continental level . He is coach of Iranian national track and field team from 2012 till now .
/wiki/Indoor_athletics_at_the_2005_Asian: Indoor athletics at the 2005 Asian Indoor Games was held in Indoor Athletics Stadium , Pattaya , Thailand from 13 November to 15 November 2005 .
/wiki/Muay_Thai_at_the_2005_Asian_Indoor: Muay Thai at the 2005 Asian Indoor Games was held in Saphan Hin Sports Complex , Phuket , Thailand from 13 November to 18 November 2005 .
/wiki/Mehdi_Shahrokhi: Seyed Mahdi Shahrokhi ( Persian : سید مهدی شاهرخی , born 23 May , 1985 ) is an Iranian athlete specializing in the shot put . He won several medals at the regional level . He has a personal best of 19.57 meters outdoors ( 2007 ) and 18.32 meters indoors ( 2009 ) .
/wiki/Hadi_Sepehrzad: Hadi Sepehrzad ( Persian : هادی سپهرزاد , born 19 January 1983 in Tehran ) is an Iranian decathlete .
/wiki/Mohsen_Rabbani: Mohammad Mohsen Rabbani ( Persian : محمدمحسن ربانی , born 18 April 1983 in Qom ) is an Iranian Pole vaulter .
/wiki/Sport_climbing_at_the_2005_Asian_I: Sport climbing at the 2005 Asian Indoor Games was held in Suphanburi Sports Complex , Suphanburi , Thailand from 14 November to 16 November 2005 .
